#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:36
msgid "Opacity Weight"
msgstr "パーティクルの不透明度の重み付け"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:37
msgid "The Opacity of all particles. Is influenced by the painting mode."
msgstr "すべての粒子の不透明度。ただし描画モードによる影響を受けます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:38
msgid "Dx Scale (Distance X Scale)"
msgstr "X速度倍率"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:39
msgid "How much the horizontal cursor distance affects the placing of the pixel. Is unstable on negative values. 1.0 is equal."
msgstr "水平方向のカーソルの移動が粒子の配置に与える影響度合い。負の数での動作は不安定です。1.0はデフォルトです。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:40
msgid "Dy Scale (Distance Y Scale)"
msgstr "Y速度倍率"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:41
msgid "How much the vertical cursor distance affects the placing of the pixel. Is unstable on negative values. 1.0 is equal."
msgstr "垂直方向のカーソルの移動が粒子の配置に与える影響度合い。負の数での動作は不安定です。1.0はデフォルトです。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:42
msgid "Gravity"
msgstr "重力"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:43
msgid "Multiplies with the previous particle's position, to find the new particle's position."
msgstr "前に置いた粒子の位置と乗算し、新しい粒子の配置位置を決定します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:45
msgid ""
"The higher, the higher the internal acceleration is, with the furthest away particle from the brush having the highest acceleration. This means that the higher iteration is, the faster and more "
"randomly a particle moves over time, giving a messier result."
msgstr "値が大きいほど、内部の加速度が大きくなり、ブラシから最も遠い粒子の加速度が最も大きくなります。つまり繰り返し処理数を多くするほど、経時的に速く、よりランダムに粒子が動き結果として複雑な描画を得ます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/particle_brush_engine.rst:46
msgid "Iterations"
msgstr "繰り返し処理数"

